summary:
• Settlement reached with NZTA on P2W project claims (COVID-19/weather delays).
  • FY25 financial impact:
  • Loss on claims receivable: ~A$16.4m (EBIT hit).
  • Cash proceeds to be received: ~A$56m.
  • Outstanding items: Insurance claims for landslips/weather damage still under negotiation.
  • No change to prior FY25 earnings outlook (except for this settlement impact).

Materiality: Non-recurring P&L/cash flow adjustment (~A$16.4m loss vs. ~A$56m inflow); resolves legacy issue.
